  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for gettext-runtime",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for gettext-runtime fixes the following issues:\n\n- Fix boo941629-unnessary-rpath-on-standard-path.patch (bsc#941629) \n- Added msgfmt-double-free.patch to fix a double free error\n  (CVE-2018-18751 bsc#1113719)\n- Add patch msgfmt-reset-msg-length-after-remove.patch\n  which does reset the length of message string after a line\n  has been removed (bsc#1106843)\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
